" Section: mapping {{{
" Wipe out all buffers
nmap <silent> <Leader>wa :1,9000bwipeout<cr>

" Toggle paste mode
nmap <silent> <Leader>p :set invpaste<CR>:set paste?<CR>

" Yank to clipboard
map <Leader>y "+y

